                                                                                                                                Input and selection

                                                                                                                                Stepper

                                                                                                                                Stable

                                                                                                                                A stepper is a component used to increase or decrease a numeric value. It typically uses plus and minus buttons to increase and decrease the value.

                                                                                                                                Usage
                                                                                                                                Specs
                                                                                                                                Status & changelog
                                                                                                                                Common alternative names
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Nudger, spin button, input stepper, numeric stepper


                                                                                                                                Questions, comments, feedback?

                                                                                                                                Leave a comment in Figma or reach out to us on Slack.

                                                                                                                                #base-design-support


                                                                                                                                Anatomy

                                                                                                                                The stepper component has two buttons on each size to increase and decreases the value in the middle.



                                                                                                                                Usage

                                                                                                                                The stepper should be used for a steady increase or decrease in value. There should always be a minimum and maximum value for the stepper. The increment value can be changed but must be the same and in whole numbers.

                                                                                                                                The stepper is most commonly used for passenger count or order item count. There's also a Time stepper specifically used for time.


                                                                                                                                Do
                                                                                                                                Always use whole numbers.
                                                                                                                                Don’t
                                                                                                                                Don't use decimals in the value. The range is too large for steppers.
                                                                                                                                Do
                                                                                                                                There should be a limit to the minimum and maximum values. It is also best to set the default value as the most commonly used value.
                                                                                                                                Don’t
                                                                                                                                Don't let the stepper go on and on without limit.



                                                                                                                                Behavior

                                                                                                                                The left button decreases the value in the middle, and the right button increases it.

                                                                                                                                States

                                                                                                                                The stepper has two buttons to adjust the value. They have the same states as the button component. However, the entire component is adjustable using gestures when using a screen reader. This means the focus state is around the whole component instead of each button.

                                                                                                                                Preloading
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                The entire stepper is replaced with the placeholder component

                                                                                                                                Enabled
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Text

                                                                                                                                contentPrimary

                                                                                                                                Enabled button

                                                                                                                                Secondary button style with backgroundSecondary background and contentPrimary icon

                                                                                                                                Disabled button

                                                                                                                                Disabled button style with backgroundStateDisabled background and contentStateDisabled icon

                                                                                                                                Focus
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Text

                                                                                                                                contentPrimary

                                                                                                                                Outlined

                                                                                                                                3px border borderAccent

                                                                                                                                Disabled
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Text

                                                                                                                                contentStateDisabled

                                                                                                                                Buttons

                                                                                                                                Disabled button style with backgroundStateDisabled background and contentStateDisabled icon

                                                                                                                                Wrapping and truncation

                                                                                                                                Typically the stepper shouldn't have a maximum value over 3 digits. However, the stepper component should be able to go as wide as its container, and then the value truncates.

                                                                                                                                Examples

                                                                                                                                Narrow

                                                                                                                                Uber Charter passenger count

                                                                                                                                Wide

                                                                                                                                Uber Eats Manager item count

                                                                                                                                Related components

                                                                                                                                Time picker
                                                                                                                                One version of the time picker uses a stepper
                                                                                                                                Slider
                                                                                                                                For larger range of values, slider might be a better choice
                                                                                                                                Select
                                                                                                                                Selecting a value in a menu of values can also be an option
                                                                                                                                Button
                                                                                                                                The stepper buttons follows the same behavior as Buttons
